{"tid":1453330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"#一個令政府減少收入方法","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:44:54.000Z","uid":291663,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7233e28f18f4c3d26fc1574d1c5b48d15cebe836","tid":1453330,"uid":291663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"#一個令政府減少收入方法<br />\n#罷買的較果不能睇小#<br />\n#除左衝，大家都要記得另一個行動。<br />\n2019年7月 <br />\n總零售業下跌30%，內地團急跌， 油尖旺行人區比反送中前 暢通，<br />\n大家可以明顯留意倒。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家8月9月10月 <br />\n只係買食物，吾買任何身外物， 連鎖店，大商戶，更加吾駛講。<br />\n除左買必須品，對零售業會有沈重打擊，政府一定會嚇到仆街，間接##收稅都少左##，當然包括香煙酒稅.<br />\n<br />\n其實買少啲野吾會死嘅，但系輸左比政府(中共)可能系一世，吾會有第二次機會， 怯你就輸一世。<br />\n借圖，借Idea <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Rw0R0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Rw0R0e.jpg&h=e4dd6949&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廣傳。"},{"pid":"113b6aaf8fe7d5dd77d8efe695acf93dffa3b557","tid":1453330,"uid":196625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"其實真係應該大規模教導市民如何逃稅, 尤其是當你個有一定收入<br />\n<br />\n哩D 野真係唔可以得有錢人知"},{"pid":"abde57fd1435f7e5d212c3eaf287b74ffe4a50dd","tid":1453330,"uid":256246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"移民"},{"pid":"927a692a46b3423e49ed4b93985d081404aa8803","tid":1453330,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:06:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">長者八達通</span></span>"},{"pid":"79517ddcfd3279bebacf9e36abd37072ee3c2a19","tid":1453330,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:09:51.000Z","msg":"遲10年報稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dded754884073af396f7cde8aa0a41ae3a511eca","tid":1453330,"uid":291663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79517ddcfd3279bebacf9e36abd37072ee3c2a19","tid":1453330,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci